## **2. Prerequisites table**

| Tool           | Version | Installation                                   |
|------          |---------|--------------                                  |
| Python         | 3.13    | https://www.python.org/downloads/              |
| Node.js        | 22.x    | https://nodejs.org                             |
| Docker Desktop | Latest  | https://www.docker.com/products/docker-desktop |
| Kubernetes     | Latest  | https://kubernetes.io                          |
| PostgreSQL     | 17      | https://www.postgresql.org/download/           |
| pgAdmin 4      | Latest  | https://www.pgadmin.org/download/              |
| Git            | Latest  | https://git-scm.com/downloads                  |
| VS Code        | Latest  | https://code.visualstudio.com/                 |
| Wireshark      | Latest  | https://www.wireshark.org/download.html        |



## **3. Setup Guide**


* **Part 1 – Clone Repository**

bash
git clone https://github.com/derrazradhwanedz/dist_sys_app.git
cd dist_sys_app

* **Part 2 – Backend Setup**

bash
cd backend
python -m venv .venv
.venv\Scripts\activate
pip install -r requirements.txt

Run backend:

bash
python server.py


* **Part 3 – Frontend Setup**

bash
cd frontend
npm install
npm run dev


* **Part 4 – Docker**

Build containers
docker compose build
Run containers

bash
docker compose up -d

Check running containers

bash
docker ps

* **Part 5 – Kubernetes**

Apply manifests

bash
kubectl apply -f k8s/

Verify resources

bash
kubectl get pods
kubectl get svc
kubectl get deployments
kubectl get ingress
kubectl get hpa


* **Part 6 – Railway Deployment**

Deploy frontend and backend to Railway.

Verify deployment by opening the Railway URLs.


* **Part 7 – Load Testing**

Run Artillery

bash
artillery run load-test.yml


## **4. Environment Variables**

| Variable          | Description                    | Source               |
|----------         |-------------                   |--------              |
| DATABASE_URL      | PostgreSQL database connection | PostgreSQL / Railway |
| SUPABASE_URL      | Supabase Project URL           | Supabase Dashboard   |
| SUPABASE_ANON_KEY | Supabase anonymous key         | Supabase Dashboard   |
| JWT_SECRET        | JWT signing secret             | Application Secret   |
| PORT              |  Backend port                  | Default 8000         |





## **5. Kubernetes Manifests**

| File                    | Description                |
|------                   |-------------               |              
| backend.yaml            |  backend application       |
| frontend.yaml           |  frontend application      |
| postgres.yaml           |  PostgreSQL database       |
| ingress.yaml            | External routing           |
| configmap.yaml          | Application configuration  |
| secret.yaml             | Sensitive configuration    |
| hpa.yaml                | Horizontal Pod Autoscaler  |
| supabase-secret.yaml    |  superbase                 |



## 6. Wireshark Filters

| Filter                        | Description             |
|---------                      |-------------            |
| tcp.flags.syn==1              | TCP Three-Way Handshake |
| http                          | HTTP GET Request        |
| http.request.method=="POST"   | HTTP POST Request       |
| tcp.flags.fin==1              | TCP Four-Way Termination|
| tls.handshake                 | TLS Handshake           |


