https://frontend-production-e3a1.up.railway.app/

Backend

https://backend-production-fb8b.up.railway.app

Important Endpoints

| Endpoint         | Method | Description           |
|----------        |--------|-------------          |
| /                | GET    | Home Page             |
| /docs            | GET    | Swagger Documentation |
| /api/v1/students | GET    | Retrieve Students     |
| /api/v1/students | POST   | Add Student           |

