## **8. Troubleshooting**

| Problem                            | Solution                                             |
|----------                          |----------                                            |
| PostgreSQL authentication failed   | Verify username, password and database configuration |
| Backend cannot connect to database | Ensure PostgreSQL container is running               |
| Railway deployment failed          | Verify environment variables and redeploy            |
| Docker container exited            | Check logs using `docker logs <container>`           |
| Kubernetes pod CrashLoopBackOff    | Check pod logs using `kubectl logs <pod-name>`       |

-

